## Third-Party Credits

This project incorporates concepts and inspiration from various sources:

### Core Tetris Implementation
- Based on community examples and M5Stack documentation
- Enhanced with modern Tetris guidelines and features

### Libraries
- M5StickCPlus2: Official M5Stack library (Apache 2.0 License)
- ESP32 WiFi: Espressif Systems (Apache 2.0 License)  
- M5GFX: M5Stack graphics library (MIT License)

### Community Contributions
- Original Tetris implementations from M5Stack community
- Network protocol concepts from ESP32 examples
- Battle system mechanics - original implementation

All third-party components retain their original licenses and copyrights.